subject: Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Harrison Barnes scored 20 points, leading No. 5 North Carolina to a 60-57 victory at home against No. 9 Wisconsin in the A.C.C./Big Ten Challenge. Jordan Taylor had 18 points to lead Wisconsin.
